channel.title: My Project
channel.description:
Well... I've been working on this signature for that passed couple of days, just screwin' around adding luminosity layers and stuff... I was told by some people it turned out okay... This is my project because I'm gunna start adding loads of shit with it... (Yea, I'm nowhere near done -.-) But this is what I've come up with Atm.
V1: [IMG]http://i283.photobucket.com/albums/kk304/_Talent_/CS.png[/img] V2: [IMG]http://i283.photobucket.com/albums/kk304/_Talent_/C0.png[/img] B&W V2: [IMG]http://i283.photobucket.com/albums/kk304/_Talent_/C1.png[/img]
Comment... I don't want ratings... Because they're either a put down or a hardcore spirit raiser (Makes me think I need no improvement...) Anyways... Yea. You can tell me what looks good or not soo good. you can suggest what too add... yea... So on and so forth...
